    </td>
    <td class="split">
          <h1>Great for Instructors</h1>
          <h3>Keep your class running smoothly and be confident that your students are getting the credit they earned. We help you discover problems as soon as they surface, so you can resolve them and focus on teaching.</h3>
        </td>
  </tr>
</table>
